Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.26,0:00:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.75,0:00:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A time machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.27,0:00:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm from the year 2036.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.72,0:00:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuha...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.67,0:00:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the time traveler
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.49,0:00:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,John Titor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:50.89,Title1,,0000,0000,0000,,Missing Link Necrosis
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.86,0:01:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The year 2036.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.03,0:01:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world was ruled by SERN...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.76,0:02:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An oppressive, totalitarian society, a dystopia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.84,0:02:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people's freedom was stolen,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they lived like zombies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.10,0:02:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who disobeyed was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.81,0:02:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was part of the resistance,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.33,0:02:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,fighting to free the world from SERN's control.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.57,0:02:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To change this dead world...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.39,0:02:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I entered the time machine my father left me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And to change the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.87,0:03:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, everything you wrote on @channel...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, most of it was true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.03,0:03:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But SERN is a research organization,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,not a ruling body.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.83,0:03:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the net, I told John Titor that many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.76,0:03:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.54,0:03:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.05,0:03:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are Chestnut Rice and Kamehameha?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.54,0:03:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Titor identified himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.96,0:03:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it wouldn't be fair not to identify myself, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.94,0:03:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll identify myself, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.07,0:03:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was using the handle Hououin Kyouma...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.17,0:03:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SERN succeeded in developing a time machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:03:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By becoming the only ones able to
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.13,0:04:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,interfere with the fourth dimension, time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.18,0:04:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they remade the entire world map.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.57,0:04:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Makise Kurisu is the person
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.84,0:04:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who contributed the most to \Nthe time machine's development.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.69,0:04:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's worshipped as the \Nmother of the time machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I worked with SERN?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.22,0:04:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.84,0:04:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I work with the kind of people who
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,perform human experiments?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what happened in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.18,0:04:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why you hated me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.51,0:04:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what about the future me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe Rintarou is a famous terrorist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Terrorist?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.33,0:04:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A terrorist who fought SERN.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're both...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.12,0:04:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,dead in the year 2036.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.11,0:04:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.63,0:04:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying something crazy like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.69,0:04:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and returning to the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.12,0:04:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.42,0:05:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to the past, to change that future.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.79,0:05:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To 1975...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1975?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.46,0:05:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SERN succeeded in developing the time machine,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.42,0:05:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,due to the time machine created \Nin 2010, in Akihabara.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the Phone Microwave?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.78,0:05:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SERN used a communications monitoring system
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.86,0:05:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to gather all the information they could \Non time machines, from around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.16,0:05:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think the first D-mail you sent tripped the system.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.82,0:05:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The message I sent in front of the Radio Building?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.91,0:05:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So if we delete the message from SERN's database,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the future will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.39,0:05:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can go to the beta world line, where SERN
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.58,0:05:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,never successfully created a time machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will that save Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.05,0:05:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.09,0:05:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we should start hacking \NSERN's database immediately...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.23,0:06:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need the IBN 5100 for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.40,0:06:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.15,0:06:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My task was to go to 1975,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.44,0:06:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,find an IBN 5100,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and get it to Okabe Rintarou.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I stayed too long, looking for my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.68,0:06:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have gone earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.99,0:06:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is everything okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.01,0:06:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.02,0:06:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.13,0:06:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.27,0:06:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll think of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.69,0:06:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.84,0:06:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as you can, run.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.62,0:06:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.80,0:06:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.48,0:06:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.68,0:06:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in the midst of an operation
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to end the Organization's schemes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.22,0:06:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a level-70 top-secret mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So stay away from this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.45,0:06:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're running.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.81,0:07:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.54,0:07:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what happened in the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,0:07:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but right now, I'm a lab member, just like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.72,0:07:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.73,0:07:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.80,0:07:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't go back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.82,0:07:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was the time machine broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it from when it crashed into the roof?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't crash.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.05,0:07:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was an error in calculating the coordinates,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.37,0:07:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where it appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.62,0:07:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I arrived, it wasn't broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.98,0:07:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then when?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:08:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had to guess, I'd say that thunderstorm we had...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.10,0:08:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might have been hit by lightning, or flooded...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.41,0:08:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.83,0:08:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I stopped you then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.33,0:08:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use the time leap machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can only use it to go back 48 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.46,0:08:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't get back to that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.37,0:08:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.16,0:08:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Kurisu-chan and Suzu-san are with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii said we should have a party to celebrate
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.10,0:08:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the time machine's completion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.41,0:08:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daru-kun and I went shopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.04,0:08:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said we were done for the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.06,0:08:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.79,0:08:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to talk about something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.32,0:08:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.61,0:08:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go home for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.48,0:08:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have the party another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.64,0:08:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't do anything dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.61,0:08:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii is worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.79,0:08:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:08:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.68,0:09:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.73,0:09:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.64,0:09:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the trains stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.17,0:09:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.40,0:09:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to repair the time machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, go back five hours ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.25,0:09:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to when the time leap machine was completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.17,0:09:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From there, go back 48 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.09,0:09:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To 2:00 PM, on the 11th.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.22,0:09:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the most time we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll finish the time machine during those two days,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.02,0:09:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't, I'll redo those two days \Nas many times as it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't to save the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.10,0:10:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a mission to save Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.81,0:10:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.11,0:10:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gather all the lab members right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I want to talk to them about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.55,0:10:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Future tech FTW.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be photoshopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.84,0:10:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you fix it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.22,0:10:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Amane, you can't do it yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.91,0:10:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too much for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.20,0:10:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father's the one who made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.46,0:10:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we can fix a time machine
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.92,0:10:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from 2036, using today's technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.34,0:10:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't know until we try.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.89,0:10:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, try and do it in two days, Daru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.75,0:10:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're our only hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.05,0:10:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why two days?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:10:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.67,0:10:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.44,0:11:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can, I'll do anything you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.02,0:11:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher, I want to have a \Nday-long date with Feyris-tan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.61,0:11:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'll make it happen somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.41,0:11:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.76,0:11:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.98,0:11:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.89,0:11:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're serious? For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.85,0:11:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.91,0:11:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.39,0:11:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.21,0:11:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more thing, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.37,0:11:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I fix it, in addition to the IBN 5100,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.08,0:11:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,get me a cel from the legendary
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.64,0:11:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1975 magical girl anime, {\i1}Ragical Girl Omit-chan!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.71,0:11:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.31,0:11:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I help, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.07,0:11:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you need to finish the time leap machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.81,0:11:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should get back to the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.00,0:11:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, aren't you all forgetting something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.62,0:11:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for Suzu-san's dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.76,0:11:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're not!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.46,0:11:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got in the time machine
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.78,0:11:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because you had a job to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.42,0:12:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but also because you wanted \Nto see your dad, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Mayushii wants to help you find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.73,0:12:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dad's name was Barrel Titor, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.33,0:12:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was his code name.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know his real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.23,0:12:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's Amane?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.65,0:12:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mom's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.12,0:12:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My only clue is this little badge he had.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.36,0:12:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dad is in 2010 Akihabara, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.31,0:12:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Mayushii will be the investigator.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina Mayuri... She's a good girl, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think you can fix it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.74,0:12:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way to say for sure yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.21,0:12:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when I looked at it, I realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.40,0:12:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of like the Phone Microwave.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:13:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's possible you can fix it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.14,0:13:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if your dad's nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.35,0:13:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He knew that we were in Akiba, in 2010, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.96,0:13:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.93,0:13:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I never heard from him directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.64,0:13:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never met him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.79,0:13:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything was in his will.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.49,0:13:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad was researching a time machine, \Nseparately from SERN...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.06,0:13:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To change the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.50,0:13:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to carry on, in his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.89,0:13:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really am sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.60,0:13:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it might be that, if I can fix the time machine,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.24,0:13:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll find your dad before you get back from 1975.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So keep this a secret from Okarin,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and try to get me that cel...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.68,0:14:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a pretty straightforward way to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Supposedly, we're the future gadget lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.04,0:14:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you don't have a more futuristic way?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.38,0:14:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing so convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.86,0:14:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Future Gadget #2, Alt. Edition,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.85,0:14:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Version 2.67.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.68,0:14:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,AKA The Bamboo Copter Camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.52,0:14:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a CCD camera on the lower body.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.35,0:14:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surprisingly sane.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.24,0:14:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could we use this for an aerial search?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.07,0:14:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The camera spins, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.76,0:14:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so the video you receive revolves at a high speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.61,0:14:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're at version 2.67, and that still isn't fixed?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.08,0:14:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the first one we've made.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.89,0:14:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daru came up with the name, along with the version.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.17,0:14:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no real meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.48,0:14:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Daru?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.44,0:14:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still there, working.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.90,0:14:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Divergence Meter...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You made it. I think you should have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.43,0:15:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this number goes above 1%, \Nthe future will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.41,0:15:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who will know,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.41,0:15:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with your Reading Steiner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.61,0:15:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I give you that, before I died in the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.71,0:15:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I've never met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.63,0:15:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were a founding member \Nof the resistance I was in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.94,0:15:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I founded a resistance?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.97,0:15:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't even save Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.15,0:15:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I kept on living!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.87,0:15:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Acting like a stupid little kid, with his fantasies?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.93,0:15:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.77,0:15:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was an honest, brave desire to save the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.50,0:16:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, mister...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.78,0:16:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am mad scientist!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.62,0:16:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.52,0:16:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonuvabitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.55,0:16:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Japanese works, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.96,0:16:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever seen this before?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.14,0:16:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know where it came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.97,0:16:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you look into it for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.85,0:16:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:17:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. It is difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure about that Japanese working?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.55,0:17:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you remember, contact me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.03,0:17:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe this will be created in the near future,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.51,0:17:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but doesn't exist now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.52,0:17:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may be fated to not meet my dad, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.83,0:17:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to give up on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.20,0:17:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're giving up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still have a day!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.97,0:17:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so mad—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.60,0:17:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to prioritize saving Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.20,0:17:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, you're a lab member and a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to help you if I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.39,0:17:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why are you already giving up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.98,0:17:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't yell at me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.85,0:17:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.89,0:17:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.71,0:17:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.10,0:17:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is she...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.22,0:17:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a kidnapping yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:18:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for the criminal. \NHe wore a badge like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.28,0:18:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.91,0:18:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.90,0:18:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.00,0:18:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.05,0:18:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was Mayushii's idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.14,0:18:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think everyone might go, "Huh?" \Nwhen they see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is operation:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.47,0:18:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Victory with Mayushii's Pamphlets!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.43,0:18:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think a kidnapping is going too far, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.63,0:18:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if the police start looking at us...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.83,0:18:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.10,0:18:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.16,0:18:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.31,0:18:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.52,0:18:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, ask me about these operations first,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.22,0:18:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,including the name...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.33,0:18:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.90,0:18:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Christina.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.77,0:19:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.19,0:19:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I learned something really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.06,0:19:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I went to buy lunch, I overheard the clerks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.35,0:19:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amane-san's dad might be a kidnapper.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.85,0:19:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.61,0:19:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,0:19:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.93,0:19:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.90,0:19:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were awesome, you would've brought me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.32,0:19:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,an ice-cold zero-calorie cola.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.66,0:19:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we fix the time machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.09,0:19:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.60,0:19:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even working this whole time, \Nthat's still amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.31,0:19:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daru's the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.54,0:19:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he looks unhealthy and kind of dim.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.67,0:19:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't judge him by his looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I've changed my mind about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.64,0:19:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you help me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.91,0:19:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, in the steaming hot confines \Nof the time machine,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.48,0:20:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can forget our shame \Nand take off our clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.99,0:20:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.68,0:20:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daru-kun and Suzu-san look good together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.19,0:20:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Together? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.68,0:20:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know how to say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.69,0:20:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.48,0:20:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri was just saying something weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.74,0:20:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if the time machine gets fixed,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.80,0:20:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried about Suzu-san when she rides it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it were for two, I could go with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.72,0:20:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you go with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.76,0:20:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why else?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.22,0:20:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd hold Suzu-san's hand really tight, and I'd say,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.11,0:20:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"It's okay! Mayushii's with you, so it's okay!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.56,0:20:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm saying this because
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.85,0:20:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I'll ever have \Nthe chance to say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.91,0:20:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? That's an exaggeration.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.63,0:20:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really grateful to you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.10,0:21:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I first came here, I didn't know anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.68,0:21:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though this era is much more peaceful,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.64,0:21:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,somehow, to me, it was really scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.32,0:21:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now I have lots of friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.31,0:21:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really happy that I could come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.45,0:21:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I could spend time with you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.31,0:21:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I could be a lab member, just for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.44,0:21:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I could spend time with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.33,0:21:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuha...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.31,0:21:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe Rintarou! Change the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.71,0:21:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it a free world, like this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.22,0:21:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuha?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.45,0:21:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.31,0:21:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.21,0:21:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mad scientist so cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.45,0:21:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy from this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.25,0:21:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remembered...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.39,0:21:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About that pin badge from yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.77,0:21:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You found her father?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.91,0:21:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.82,0:21:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
